pageProduct.name: Plunkett's Vita E Natural Vitamin E Quick Dry Oil 125ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Plunkett's Vita E Natural Vitamin E Quick Dry Oil contains high potency (100IU) Vitamin E and is enriched with Rosehip Oil and Infused with Mandarin Oil.

This fast absorbing oil, based on natural Vitamin E provides deep hydration whilst locking moisutre in. It helps restore damaged skin and softens scars and stretchimarks, leaving no oily residue.

Suitable For: Ideal for Dry, damaged skin, Stretchmarks and scars.

Size: 125mL

KEY FEATURES

• Vitamin E: helps skin retain natural moisture and eases dryness while antioxidants neutralise damaging free radicals generated by the environment. Softens and smoothes skin by replenishing moisure.
• Rosehip Oil: is rich in Vitamin A & C and essential fatty acids (Omega 3 & 6), helping to improve skin elasticity and suppleness.
• Mandarin Oil: is useful in helping reduce acne, brighten skin and diminish the apprearance of scars and wrinkles.

Warnings

For external use only. Store below 30°C

Ingredients

Helianthus Annus, Vitus Vinefera (Grapeseed Oil), Tocopheryl Acetate 100IU/gram (Vitamin E), Rosa Canina (Rosehip Oil), Citrus Nobilis (Mandarin Oil).

Active Ingredients: Natural Vitamin E (100 IU per gram)
Rosehip Oil
Mandarin Oil

Directions

Gently massage into skin as often as neeed. Ideal for face an body. For all skin types.
